==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: organelle
<hw>organelle</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>a specialized
part of a cell performing a specific function, usually visible under the
microscope as a distinct object; it is analogous to an organ{2}, but on
a microscopic scale.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> cell organ.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Organic</ent>⟦br⟧
